In which variable is stored the data sent via an html form using the GET method ? ----- $_GET

When submitting a form using the POST method, the variables values appear in the URL. True or False? ----- False 

What is the difference between $a=$b and $a==$b ? ----- 1. comparing the variable 2.compare a with b.if equal return a boolean value true.else return false.

What character must be at the end of each line of php code ? ------ (; semicolon) 

