What will this script return at 10h23 AM ? ----- Hello!
$hour = date('H');
if ($hour > 17){
	echo "Good evening!";
} elseif ($hour > 13){
	echo "Good afternoon!";
} else{
	echo "Hello!";
}
... And what will it return at 15h02 AM ? ----- Good afternoon!

